    <item>
      <title>朝鲜情报机构称金正恩体重增加 寻求药物治疗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-29/north-korean-officials-looking-for-medicines-for-kim-s-obesity-related-health-problems-seoul-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社）——韩国情报机构周一向议员表示，朝鲜领导人金正恩已恢复体重，并似乎患有高血压和糖尿病等与肥胖相关的健康问题，他的官员正在国外寻找新药来治疗这些疾病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-29/north-korean-officials-looking-for-medicines-for-kim-s-obesity-related-health-problems-seoul-says</guid>
